лIN TREASURED MEMORY OF MY DARLING HUSBAND
FRANIE DANIELS 25.10.1910 - 15.2.1992
HIS BUSINESS WAS IN MOUNT STREET
TOGETHER WE SHARED THIS SECRET GARDEN
FOR EVER AND ALWAYS AND ALL ETERNITY YOUR SHELAGH"о
лPeter & Muriel Kenny
We wrote your name In the sand, but the waves washed it away
We wrote your name in the sky, but the clouds blew it away
So we wrote your name in our hearts and forever it will stay"ь
уIn celebration of the marriage of
Dan Moss and Claudie Sellers
18th July 2015
So, she leaning on her husband's arm, they turned homeward
by a rosy path which the gracious sun struck out for them in its setting"з
